\f0\b\fs34 \cf3 Vision:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\i\b0\fs30 \cf0 An app that helps user be up-to-date with news at TUT.by
\f1\i0 .\
Application allows to subscribe to different feeds at tut.by, load them into a local database and display an aggregated list of news in a Table View.\
Each piece of news can be in one the states:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}new - 
\f2\i item is new and was not read yet
\f3\i0\fs24 \
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\fs30 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}reading - 
\f2\i item is being read. user opened it at least once but didn't finish reading, so he will want to continue reading later
\f3\i0\fs24 \
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\fs30 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}done - 
\f2\i item is already read. user is done with it and it should not be displayed in the list (or should be greyed out).
\f3\i0\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs30 \cf0 User can setup application to delete old items from database. Using settings user can choose 1 week, 1 month and 3 months for the time to keep "done" items in the DB. (and app will not save any "new" items that are older then this setting)\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

