\f0\b\fs30 \cf3 v.2.1. Item states\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When user opens an item app automatically marks it "reading" so that user will see it differently in the list.
\f3\fs24 \
\ls8\ilvl0
